review_blob: Great Stout, sweet taste, goes down smooth with a slightly bitter after taste. Not worth the $16-20 every day, but it did go to space. My wife and I would buy this every day if it was $3-5, yumm.
Great taste, very milky smooth, best part is the sweet bite. Not too sweet and not to much bitterness, perfect for my taste
beer_name: Wild Ride Stand Up and Shout Stout
